## 0.189
 - new updating system: springlobby downloads the update file and extracts it. then it runs springlobby_updater which updates all files and re-runs springlobby. no more waiting for springlobby_updater to download. also the update-urls can be configured, this allows to select updates from the develop branch.
 - fix tab selection at start
 - fix some unicode path problems (win32 only)
 - allow battles to be joined without spring/unitsync installed
 - made faction icon transparent
 - always show "user left" when he was active before (=wrote sth.)[/list]

